Pre-made components

We provide a set of UI components that are ready to use out of the box. You can also extend or customize them to fit your needs.

Dynamic color palettes

By using our built-in color system, you can easily create dynamic color palettes for your application, and even change them on the fly.

Consistent branding

Keep your branding consistent across your entire application with our built-in theming system.
